Stiffness: The spring strength of the drive. Force proportional to the position error.
Damping: The damping strength of the drive. Force proportional to the velocity error.
MaxForce: The force limit of the drive.
bEnablePositionDrive: Enables/Disables position drive (orientation if using angular drive)
bEnableVelocityDrive: Enables/Disables velocity drive (angular velocity if using angular drive)
